<subSubSection pageId="148" pageNumber="546" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph blockId="148.[177,1385,290,836]" pageId="148" pageNumber="546">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[180,291,290,323]" pageId="148" pageNumber="546">Habitat.</emphasis>
Found in undisturbed and slightly disturbed montane forests, with moistsoil, at elevations of 1500-2086 m. Phillips's Congo Shrews have also been recorded in bamboo forests and marshy habitats.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
