<subSubSection pageId="148" pageNumber="546" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="148.[177,1385,290,836]" pageId="148" pageNumber="546">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[178,416,487,520]" pageId="148" pageNumber="546">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
Phillips's Congo Shrews are terrestrial and primarily nocturnal, although they can also be found during the day.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
